WIKIARK.ORG
############################
Internal Webserver based on perl's Mojolicious

The purpose is offer the local network a file-share for heterogenous machines
unix box : mojolicious : any web-interface device

The unix box will have access to encrypted & network file shares both local and external.
The gui web-interface-device will have access to files via a simple internal website

This mojolicious web server provides a work around and also a alternate file-exchange method which adds both roboustness & heterogenity to a network.
